#. SLE/patterns-gnome/patterns-gnome-gnome/summary
msgid "GNOME Desktop Environment (Wayland)"
msgstr "Lingkungan Desktop GNOME (Wayland)"

#. SLE/patterns-gnome/patterns-gnome-gnome/description
msgid ""
"The GNOME desktop environment is an intuitive and attractive desktop for "
"users. This pattern installs components for GNOME to run with Wayland and "
"X11 technologies."
msgstr ""
"Lingkungan desktop GNOME adalah lingkungan desktop yang intuitif dan menarik "
"bagi pengguna. Pola ini menginstal komponen untuk menjalankan GNOME dengan "
"teknologi Wayland dan X11."

#. SLE/patterns-gnome/patterns-gnome-gnome/category
#. SLE/patterns-gnome/patterns-gnome-gnome_imaging/category
#. SLE/patterns-gnome/patterns-gnome-gnome_multimedia/category
msgid "GNOME Desktop"
msgstr "Lingkungan Desktop GNOME"

#. SLE/patterns-gnome/patterns-gnome-gnome_imaging/summary
msgid "GNOME Graphics"
msgstr "Grafik GNOME"

#. SLE/patterns-gnome/patterns-gnome-gnome_imaging/description
msgid "Handling of digital photos and graphics"
msgstr "Pengelolaan foto digital dan grafis"

#. SLE/patterns-gnome/patterns-gnome-gnome_multimedia/summary
#. SLE/patterns-gnome/patterns-gnome-gnome_multimedia/description
msgid "GNOME Multimedia"
msgstr "GNOME Multimedia"

#. SLE/patterns-gnome/patterns-gnome-gnome_x11/summary
msgid "GNOME Desktop Environment (X11)"
msgstr "Lingkungan Desktop GNOME (X11)"

#. SLE/patterns-gnome/patterns-gnome-gnome_x11/description
msgid ""
"The GNOME desktop environment is an intuitive and attractive desktop for "
"users. This pattern installs a full featured GNOME desktop environment, "
"including Office suite, E-Mail client, Web Browser, File Manager, running "
"with X11 technology."
msgstr ""
"Lingkungan desktop GNOME adalah lingkungan desktop yang intuitif dan menarik "
"bagi pengguna. Pola ini menginstal lingkungan desktop GNOME yang lengkap, "
"termasuk paket perkantoran, klien email, peramban web, dan pengelola file, "
"yang berjalan dengan teknologi X11."

#. SLE/patterns-gnome/patterns-gnome-gnome_x11/category
msgid "Graphical Environments"
msgstr "Lingkungan Grafis"

#. SLE/patterns-office/patterns-office-office/summary
msgid "Office Software"
msgstr "Perangkat Lunak Kantor"

#. SLE/patterns-office/patterns-office-office/description
msgid "Office software for your desktop environment including LibreOffice."
msgstr ""
"Perangkat lunak kantor untuk lingkungan desktop Anda, termasuk LibreOffice."

#. SLE/patterns-ha-geo/patterns-ha-geo-ha_geo/summary
msgid "GEO Clustering for High Availability"
msgstr "Pengelompokan GEO untuk Ketersediaan Tinggi"

#. SLE/patterns-ha-geo/patterns-ha-geo-ha_geo/description
msgid ""
"This pattern provides tools for building multi-site clustering setups based "
"on the SUSE Linux Enterprise High-Availability and its GEO extension."
msgstr ""
"Pola ini menyediakan alat untuk membangun konfigurasi kluster multi-situs "
"berdasarkan SUSE Linux Enterprise High-Availability dan ekstensi GEO-nya."

#. SLE/patterns-ha-geo/patterns-ha-geo-ha_geo/category
#. SLE/patterns-ha/patterns-ha-ha_sles/category
msgid "Primary Functions"
msgstr "Fungsi Primer"

#. SLE/patterns-ha/patterns-ha-ha_sles/summary
msgid "High Availability"
msgstr "High Availability"

#. SLE/patterns-ha/patterns-ha-ha_sles/description
msgid ""
"Provide tools to ensure a high degree of operational continuity and reduce "
"the downtimes of your system."
msgstr ""
"Menyediakan tool untuk memastikan tingkat operasional terus menerus dan "
"mengurangi sistem downtime."

#. SLE/patterns-lp/patterns-lp-lp_sles/summary
msgid "Live Patching"
msgstr "Patching Langsung"

#. SLE/patterns-lp/patterns-lp-lp_sles/description
msgid "Provide tools and patches to fix kernel at runtime."
msgstr "Sediakan alat dan tambalan untuk memperbaiki kernel saat runtime."

#. SLE/patterns-gnome/patterns-gnome-gnome_basic/summary
msgid "GNOME Desktop Environment (Basic)"
msgstr "Lingkungan Desktop GNOME (Dasar)"

#. SLE/patterns-gnome/patterns-gnome-gnome_basic/description
msgid ""
"The GNOME desktop environment is an intuitive and attractive desktop for "
"users. This pattern installs GNOME desktop environment with only essential "
"graphical applications installed (File Manager, Web Browser)."
msgstr ""
"Lingkungan desktop GNOME adalah lingkungan desktop yang intuitif dan menarik "
"bagi pengguna. Pola ini menginstal lingkungan desktop GNOME dengan hanya "
"aplikasi grafis esensial yang diinstal (Manajer File, Peramban Web)."

#. SLE/patterns-gnome/patterns-gnome-gnome_basis/summary
msgid "GNOME Base System"
msgstr "Sistem Dasar GNOME"

#. SLE/patterns-gnome/patterns-gnome-gnome_basis/description
msgid "Base packages for the GNOME desktop environment."
msgstr "Paket dasar untuk lingkungan desktop GNOME."

#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-apparmor/summary
#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-apparmor-32bit/summary
msgid "AppArmor"
msgstr "AppArmor"

#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-apparmor/description
msgid ""
"AppArmor is an application security framework that provides mandatory access "
"control for programs. It protects from exploitation of software flaws and "
"compromised systems. It offers an advanced tool set that automates the "
"development of per-program application security without requiring additional "
"knowledge."
msgstr ""
"AppArmor adalah kerangka kerja keamanan aplikasi yang menyediakan kontrol "
"akses wajib untuk program. Ia melindungi dari eksploitasi celah keamanan "
"perangkat lunak dan sistem yang terkompromi. Ia menawarkan kumpulan alat "
"canggih yang mengotomatisasi pengembangan keamanan aplikasi per program "
"tanpa memerlukan pengetahuan tambahan."

#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-apparmor-32bit/description
msgid "The 32bit pattern complementing apparmor."
msgstr "Aplikasi pelengkap AppArmor dengan pola 32-bit."

#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-base/summary
#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-base-32bit/summary
#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-minimal_base/summary
#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-minimal_base-32bit/summary
msgid "Base System"
msgstr "Sistem Dasar"

#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-base/description
#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-basesystem/description
msgid ""
"This is the base runtime system.  It contains only a minimal multiuser "
"booting system. For running on real hardware, you need to add additional "
"packages and pattern to make this pattern useful on its own."
msgstr ""
"Ini adalah sistem runtime dasar. Yang hanya mengandung sebuah sistem booting "
"multiuser minimal. Untuk menjalankan pada hardware nyata, kamu perlu "
"menambahkan paket-paket tambahan untuk membuat pola ini berguna."

#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-base-32bit/description
msgid "The 32bit pattern complementing base."
msgstr "Pola 32-bit yang melengkapi basis."

#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-basesystem/summary
msgid "Base System (alias pattern for base)"
msgstr "Sistem Dasar (alias pola untuk dasar)"

#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-documentation/summary
#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-documentation/description
msgid "Help and Support Documentation"
msgstr "Dokumentasi Help dan Support"

#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-enhanced_base/summary
#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-enhanced_base-32bit/summary
msgid "Enhanced Base System"
msgstr "Sistem Dasar yang Ditingkatkan"

#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-enhanced_base/description
msgid ""
"This is the enhanced base runtime system with lots of convenience packages."
msgstr ""
"Ini adalah sistem runtime dasar yang ditingkatkan dengan banyak paket "
"kemudahan."

#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-enhanced_base-32bit/description
msgid "The 32bit pattern complementing enhanced_base."
msgstr "Pola 32-bit yang melengkapi enhanced_base."

#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-minimal_base/description
msgid ""
"This is the minimal SLE runtime system. It is really a minimal system, you "
"can login and a shell will be started, that's all. It is intended as base "
"for Appliances."
msgstr ""
"Ini adalah sistem runtime SLE minimal. Ini benar-benar sistem minimal, Anda "
"dapat masuk dan shell akan dijalankan, itu saja. Sistem ini dirancang "
"sebagai dasar untuk Appliances."

#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-minimal_base-32bit/description
msgid "The 32bit pattern complementing minimal_base."
msgstr "Pola 32-bit yang melengkapi minimal_base."

#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-sw_management/summary
#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-sw_management-32bit/summary
msgid "Software Management"
msgstr "Manajemen Perangkat Lunak"

#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-sw_management/description
msgid ""
"This pattern provides a graphical application and a command line tool for "
"keeping your system up to date."
msgstr ""
"Pola ini menyediakan aplikasi grafis dan alat baris perintah untuk menjaga "
"sistem Anda tetap diperbarui."

#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-sw_management-32bit/description
msgid "The 32bit pattern complementing sw_management."
msgstr "Pola 32-bit yang melengkapi sw_management."

#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-x11/summary
#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-x11-32bit/summary
#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-x11_enhanced/summary
#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-x11_enhanced-32bit/summary
msgid "X Window System"
msgstr "X Window System"

#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-x11/description
#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-x11_enhanced/description
msgid ""
"The X Window System provides the only standard platform-independent "
"networked graphical window system bridging the heterogeneous platforms in "
"today's enterprise: from network servers to desktops, thin clients, laptops, "
"and handhelds, independent of operating system and hardware."
msgstr ""
"Sistem Jendela X menyediakan platform grafis jendela jaringan yang standar "
"dan independen dari platform, yang menghubungkan platform-platform heterogen "
"dalam lingkungan perusahaan saat ini: mulai dari server jaringan hingga "
"desktop, thin client, laptop, dan perangkat genggam, tanpa tergantung pada "
"sistem operasi dan perangkat keras."

#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-x11-32bit/description
msgid "The 32bit pattern complementing x11."
msgstr "Pola 32-bit yang melengkapi x11."

#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-x11_enhanced-32bit/description
msgid "The 32bit pattern complementing x11_enhanced."
msgstr "Pola 32-bit yang melengkapi x11_enhanced."

#. SLE/patterns-devel-base/patterns-devel-base-devel_basis/description
msgid "Minimal set of tools for compiling and linking applications."
msgstr "Seperangkat alat minimal untuk mengkompilasi dan menautkan aplikasi."

#. SLE/patterns-fonts/patterns-fonts-fonts/summary
msgid "Fonts"
msgstr "Font"

#. SLE/patterns-fonts/patterns-fonts-fonts/description
msgid "Base fonts and font configuration."
msgstr "Font dasar dan konfigurasi font."

#. SLE/patterns-yast/patterns-yast-x11_yast/summary
msgid "YaST User Interfaces"
msgstr "Antarmuka Pengguna YaST"

#. SLE/patterns-yast/patterns-yast-x11_yast/description
msgid "Graphical YaST user interfaces for minimal X desktop."
msgstr "Antarmuka pengguna YaST grafis untuk desktop X minimal."

#. SLE/patterns-yast/patterns-yast-yast2_basis/summary
msgid "YaST System Administration"
msgstr "YaST Administrasi Sistem"

#. SLE/patterns-yast/patterns-yast-yast2_basis/description
msgid "YaST tools for basic system administration."
msgstr "Alat YaST untuk administrasi sistem dasar."

#. SLE/patterns-ofed/patterns-ofed-ofed/summary
#. SLE/patterns-ofed/patterns-ofed-ofed-32bit/summary
msgid "Infiniband (OFED)"
msgstr "Infiniband (OFED)"

#. SLE/patterns-ofed/patterns-ofed-ofed/description
msgid ""
"This pattern defines the OpenFabrics Enterprise Distribution (OFED) software "
"base packages. The base pattern includes the packages you need to get your "
"Infiniband adapter operational, that is IB kernel modules and basic user "
"level libraries."
msgstr ""
"Pola ini mendefinisikan paket perangkat lunak dasar OpenFabrics Enterprise "
"Distribution (OFED). Pola dasar ini mencakup paket-paket yang diperlukan "
"untuk mengaktifkan adaptor Infiniband Anda, yaitu modul kernel IB dan "
"perpustakaan tingkat pengguna dasar."

#. SLE/patterns-ofed/patterns-ofed-ofed-32bit/description
msgid "The 32bit pattern complementing ofed."
msgstr "Pola 32-bit yang melengkapi ofed."

#. SLE/patterns-rpm-macros/summary
msgid "RPM macros for building of patterns modules"
msgstr "Makro RPM untuk pembuatan modul pola"

#. SLE/patterns-rpm-macros/description
msgid "This package contains SUSE RPM macros to aid creating patterns."
msgstr "Paket ini berisi makro SUSE RPM untuk membantu dalam pembuatan pola."

#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-dhcp_dns_server/summary
#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-dhcp_dns_server-32bit/summary
msgid "DHCP and DNS Server"
msgstr "Server DHCP dan DNS"

#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-dhcp_dns_server/description
msgid ""
"Software to set up a server for the Dynamic Host Configuration Protocol "
"(DHCP) and the Domain Name System (DNS) services. DHCP provides "
"configuration parameters to client computers to integrate them into a "
"network, whereas DNS delivers information associated with domain names, in "
"particular, the IP address."
msgstr ""
"Perangkat lunak untuk mengonfigurasi server untuk Protokol Konfigurasi Host "
"Dinamis (DHCP) dan Layanan Sistem Nama Domain (DNS). DHCP menyediakan "
"parameter konfigurasi kepada komputer klien untuk mengintegrasikannya ke "
"dalam jaringan, sedangkan DNS menyediakan informasi yang terkait dengan nama "
"domain, khususnya alamat IP."

#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-dhcp_dns_server/category
#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-directory_server/category
#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-file_server/category
#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-gateway_server/category
#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-kvm_server/category
#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-lamp_server/category
#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-mail_server/category
#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-printing/category
msgid "Server Functions"
msgstr "Fungsi Server"

#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-dhcp_dns_server-32bit/description
msgid "The 32bit pattern complementing dhcp_dns_server."
msgstr "Pola 32-bit yang melengkapi dhcp_dns_server."

#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-directory_server/summary
#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-directory_server-32bit/summary
msgid "Directory Server (LDAP)"
msgstr "Server Direktori (LDAP)"

#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-directory_server/description
msgid ""
"Software to set up a directory server with OpenLDAP. The Lightweight "
"Directory Access Protocol (LDAP) is used to access online directory services."
msgstr ""
"Perangkat lunak untuk mengonfigurasi server direktori menggunakan OpenLDAP. "
"Lightweight Directory Access Protocol (LDAP) digunakan untuk mengakses "
"layanan direktori online."

#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-directory_server-32bit/description
msgid "The 32bit pattern complementing directory_server."
msgstr "Pola 32-bit yang melengkapi direktori server."

#. SLE/patterns-server-enterprise/patterns-server-enterprise-fips/summary
#. SLE/patterns-server-enterprise/patterns-server-enterprise-fips-32bit/summary
msgid "FIPS 140-2 specific packages"
msgstr "Paket-paket khusus FIPS 140-2"

#. SLE/patterns-server-enterprise/patterns-server-enterprise-fips/description
msgid ""
"This pattern installs the FIPS 140-2 specific packages that complete the "
"various cryptographic modules in use. It is required if you want to run the "
"machine with \"fips=1\".\n"
"\n"
"Please note that this pattern only enables FIPS 140-2 compliant operation, "
"it does not directly make the system FIPS 140-2 certified nor validated.\n"
"\n"
"Please refer to SUSE official statements on the state of FIPS 140-2 "
"certification."
msgstr ""
"Pola ini menginstal paket-paket khusus FIPS 140-2 yang melengkapi berbagai "
"modul kriptografi yang digunakan. Pola ini diperlukan jika Anda ingin "
"menjalankan mesin dengan opsi “fips=1”.\n"
"\n"
"Harap diperhatikan bahwa pola ini hanya mengaktifkan operasi yang sesuai "
"dengan FIPS 140-2, namun tidak secara langsung membuat sistem menjadi "
"bersertifikat atau tervalidasi FIPS 140-2.\n"
"\n"
"Silakan merujuk pada pernyataan resmi SUSE mengenai status sertifikasi FIPS "
"140-2."

#. SLE/patterns-server-enterprise/patterns-server-enterprise-fips-32bit/description
msgid "The 32bit pattern complementing fips."
msgstr "Pola 32-bit yang melengkapi FIPs."

#. SLE/patterns-server-enterprise/patterns-server-enterprise-hwcrypto/summary
msgid "System z HW crypto support"
msgstr "Dukungan kriptografi perangkat keras (HW) untuk sistem z"

#. SLE/patterns-server-enterprise/patterns-server-enterprise-hwcrypto/description
msgid ""
"A selection of packages that installs the System z HW crypto stack on System "
"z."
msgstr ""
"Pilihan paket yang mememasang stack kriptografi perangkat keras (HW crypto "
"stack) pada sistem System z."

#. SLE/patterns-server-enterprise/patterns-server-enterprise-oracle_server/summary
#. SLE/patterns-server-enterprise/patterns-server-enterprise-oracle_server-32bit/summary
msgid "Oracle Server Base"
msgstr "Oracle Server Base"

#. SLE/patterns-server-enterprise/patterns-server-enterprise-oracle_server/description
msgid "Set up the server for installing Oracle databases."
msgstr "Setup server untuk instalasi database Oracle."

#. SLE/patterns-server-enterprise/patterns-server-enterprise-oracle_server-32bit/description
msgid "The 32bit pattern complementing oracle_server."
msgstr "Pola 32-bit yang melengkapi oracle_server."

#. SLE/patterns-server-enterprise/patterns-server-enterprise-sap_server/summary
#. SLE/patterns-server-enterprise/patterns-server-enterprise-sap_server-32bit/summary
msgid "SAP Application Server Base"
msgstr "SAP Application Server Base"

#. SLE/patterns-server-enterprise/patterns-server-enterprise-sap_server/description
msgid "Set up the server for installing SAP systems."
msgstr "Setup server untuk instalasi sistem SAP."

#. SLE/patterns-server-enterprise/patterns-server-enterprise-sap_server-32bit/description
msgid "The 32bit pattern complementing sap_server."
msgstr "Pola 32-bit yang melengkapi sap_server."

#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-file_server/summary
#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-file_server-32bit/summary
msgid "File Server"
msgstr "Server File"

#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-file_server/description
msgid ""
"File services to host files so that they may be accessed or retrieved by "
"other computers on the same network. This includes the FTP, SMB, and NFS "
"protocols."
msgstr ""
"Layanan file untuk menyimpan file sehingga dapat diakses atau diambil oleh "
"komputer lain di jaringan yang sama. Ini mencakup protokol FTP, SMB, dan NFS."

#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-file_server-32bit/description
msgid "The 32bit pattern complementing file_server."
msgstr "Pola 32-bit yang melengkapi file_server."

#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-gateway_server/summary
#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-gateway_server-32bit/summary
msgid "Internet Gateway"
msgstr "Gateway Internet"

#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-gateway_server/description
msgid ""
"Software to set up a proxy, firewall, and gateway server, including a "
"virtual private network (VPN) gateway."
msgstr ""
"Perangkat lunak untuk mengonfigurasi server proxy, firewall, dan gateway, "
"termasuk gateway jaringan pribadi virtual (VPN)."

#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-gateway_server-32bit/description
msgid "The 32bit pattern complementing gateway_server."
msgstr "Pola 32-bit yang melengkapi gateway_server."

#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-kvm_server/summary
msgid "KVM Host Server"
msgstr "Server Host KVM"

#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-kvm_server/description
msgid ""
"Software to set up a server for configuring, managing, and monitoring "
"virtual machines on a single physical machine."
msgstr ""
"Perangkat lunak untuk mengonfigurasi, mengelola, dan memantau mesin virtual "
"pada satu mesin fisik."

#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-kvm_tools/summary
msgid "KVM Virtualization Host and tools"
msgstr "Host Virtualisasi KVM dan alat-alatnya"

#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-kvm_tools/description
msgid ""
"This will provide all minimal system to get a running KVM Hypervisor and be "
"able to configure, manage, and monitor virtual machines on a single physical "
"machine."
msgstr ""
"Ini akan memberikan semua sistem minimal untuk menjalankan Hypervisor KVM "
"dan dapat mengonfigurasi, mengelola, dan memantau mesin virtual pada satu "
"mesin fisik."

#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-lamp_server/summary
#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-lamp_server-32bit/summary
msgid "Web and LAMP Server"
msgstr "Server Web LAMP"

#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-lamp_server/description
msgid ""
"Software to set up a Web server that is able to serve static, dynamic, and "
"interactive content (like a Web shop). This includes Apache HTTP Server, the "
"database management system MySQL, and scripting languages such as PHP, "
"Python, Ruby on Rails, or Perl."
msgstr ""
"Perangkat lunak untuk mengonfigurasi server web yang mampu menyajikan konten "
"statis, dinamis, dan interaktif (seperti toko online). Ini mencakup Apache "
"HTTP Server, sistem manajemen basis data MySQL, dan bahasa pemrograman skrip "
"seperti PHP, Python, Ruby on Rails, atau Perl."

#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-lamp_server-32bit/description
msgid "The 32bit pattern complementing lamp_server."
msgstr "Pola 32-bit yang melengkapi lamp_server."

#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-mail_server/summary
#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-mail_server-32bit/summary
msgid "Mail and News Server"
msgstr "Server Mail dan News"

#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-mail_server/description
msgid ""
"Software to set up electronic mail and message services to handle email, "
"mailing, and news lists, including a virus scanner to scan messages at the "
"server level."
msgstr ""
"Perangkat lunak untuk mengonfigurasi layanan surat elektronik dan pesan "
"untuk mengelola email, pengiriman surat, dan daftar berita, termasuk "
"pemindai virus untuk memindai pesan di tingkat server."

#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-mail_server-32bit/description
msgid "The 32bit pattern complementing mail_server."
msgstr "Pola 32-bit yang melengkapi mail_server."

#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-printing/summary
#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-printing-32bit/summary
msgid "Print Server"
msgstr "Print Server"

#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-printing/description
msgid ""
"This pattern provides all packages necessary for printing. It provides all "
"needed packages for printing to a locally connected printer, printing using "
"a remote print server and for setting up a print server."
msgstr ""
"Pola ini menyediakan semua paket yang diperlukan untuk mencetak. Pola ini "
"menyediakan semua paket yang diperlukan untuk mencetak ke printer yang "
"terhubung secara lokal, mencetak menggunakan server cetak jarak jauh, dan "
"untuk mengatur server cetak."

#. SLE/patterns-server/patterns-server-printing-32bit/description
msgid "The 32bit pattern complementing printing."
msgstr "Pola 32-bit yang melengkapi pencetakan."

#. SLE/patterns-wbem/patterns-wbem-WBEM-32bit/summary
msgid "Web-Based Enterprise Management"
msgstr "Manajemen Enterprise Berbasis Web"

#. SLE/patterns-wbem/patterns-wbem-WBEM-32bit/description
msgid "The 32bit pattern complementing WBEM."
msgstr "Pola 32-bit yang melengkapi WBEM."

#. SLE/patterns-yast/patterns-yast-yast2_install_wf/summary
msgid "YaST Installation Packages"
msgstr "Paket Instalasi YaST"

#. SLE/patterns-yast/patterns-yast-yast2_install_wf/description
msgid "YaST tools for installing your system."
msgstr "Alat YaST untuk menginstal sistem Anda."

#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-32bit/summary
msgid "32-Bit Runtime Environment"
msgstr "Lingkungan Runtime 32-Bit"

#. SLE/patterns-base/patterns-base-32bit/description
msgid ""
"This will install the 32-bit variant of all selected patterns. This allows "
"to execute 32-bit software."
msgstr ""
"Ini akan menginstal varian 32-bit dari semua pola yang dipilih. Hal ini "
"memungkinkan untuk menjalankan perangkat lunak 32-bit."

#. SLE/patterns-hpc/patterns-hpc-compute_node/summary
msgid "HPC Basic Compute Node"
msgstr "Node Komputasi Dasar HPC"

#. SLE/patterns-hpc/patterns-hpc-compute_node/description
msgid ""
"A compute node comprises of a minimal software image and mainly runs "
"simulation programs. Services on this node should be reduced to a bare "
"minimum and the node *must* be installed in a automatic manner. The pattern "
"'HPC modularized libraries' should also be installed."
msgstr ""
"Sebuah node komputasi terdiri dari citra perangkat lunak minimal dan "
"terutama menjalankan program simulasi. Layanan pada node ini harus dikurangi "
"hingga seminimal mungkin, dan node *harus* dipasang secara otomatis. Pola ‘"
"Perpustakaan HPC yang dimodularisasi’ juga harus dipasang."

#. SLE/patterns-hpc/patterns-hpc-development_node/summary
msgid "HPC Development Packages"
msgstr "Paket Pengembangan HPC"

#. SLE/patterns-hpc/patterns-hpc-development_node/description
msgid ""
"This package provides all the relevant packages for developing HPC "
"applications. It depends on the pattern 'HPC modularized libraries'. In "
"addition it includes the GNU compilers and the relevant management packages."
msgstr ""
"Paket ini menyediakan semua paket yang relevan untuk mengembangkan aplikasi "
"HPC. Paket ini bergantung pada pola ‘Perpustakaan HPC yang dimodularisasi’. "
"Selain itu, paket ini juga mencakup kompiler GNU dan paket manajemen yang "
"relevan."

#. SLE/patterns-hpc/patterns-hpc-libraries/summary
msgid "HPC modularized Libraries"
msgstr "Pustaka termodularisasi HPC"

#. SLE/patterns-hpc/patterns-hpc-libraries/description
msgid ""
"This package provides all the modularized libraries so that they can be used "
"in an HPC environment. These libraries allow to install several MPI flavors "
"in parallel. In order to use thess libraries one needs to load them via the "
"module command first."
msgstr ""
"Paket ini menyediakan semua perpustakaan modular sehingga dapat digunakan "
"dalam lingkungan HPC. Perpustakaan-perpustakaan ini memungkinkan pemasangan "
"beberapa varian MPI secara paralel. Untuk menggunakan perpustakaan-"
"perpustakaan ini, pengguna perlu memuatnya terlebih dahulu melalui perintah "
"module."

#. SLE/patterns-hpc/patterns-hpc-workload_server/summary
msgid "HPC Workload Manager"
msgstr "Manajer Beban Kerja HPC"

#. SLE/patterns-hpc/patterns-hpc-workload_server/description
msgid ""
"This package provides all the relevant packages for running the central "
"server component of the slurm workload manager."
msgstr ""
"Paket ini menyediakan semua paket yang diperlukan untuk menjalankan komponen "
"server pusat dari manajer beban kerja Slurm."

#. SLE/patterns-public-cloud-15/patterns-public-cloud-15-Amazon-Web-Services/summary
msgid "Amazon Web Services - All"
msgstr "Amazon Web Services - Semua"

#. SLE/patterns-public-cloud-15/patterns-public-cloud-15-Amazon-Web-Services/description
msgid ""
"This pattern installs all Amazon Web Services command line interface tools, "
"instance initialization packages and tools to communicate with the cloud "
"framework from within a running instance. It is not recommended to install "
"this pattern, but instead install one of the use-case specific patterns (e."
"g. Amazon Web Services - Tools)."
msgstr ""
"Pola ini menginstal semua alat antarmuka baris perintah Amazon Web Services, "
"paket inisialisasi instance, dan alat untuk berkomunikasi dengan kerangka "
"kerja cloud dari dalam instance yang sedang berjalan. Tidak disarankan untuk "
"menginstal pola ini, melainkan instal salah satu pola yang spesifik untuk "
"kasus penggunaan (misalnya Amazon Web Services - Tools)."

#. SLE/patterns-public-cloud-15/patterns-public-cloud-15-Amazon-Web-Services-Instance-Init/summary
msgid "Amazon Web Services - Instance Initialization"
msgstr "Amazon Web Services - Inisialisasi Instance"

#. SLE/patterns-public-cloud-15/patterns-public-cloud-15-Amazon-Web-Services-Instance-Init/description
msgid ""
"This pattern installs the Amazon Web Services instance initialization "
"packages which support the provisioning and running of instances in the "
"cloud framework (e.g. cloud-init)."
msgstr ""
"Pola ini menginstal paket inisialisasi instance Amazon Web Services yang "
"mendukung penyediaan dan pengoperasian instance dalam kerangka kerja cloud ("
"misalnya cloud-init)."

#. SLE/patterns-public-cloud-15/patterns-public-cloud-15-Amazon-Web-Services-Instance-Tools/summary
msgid "Amazon Web Services - Instance Tools"
msgstr "Amazon Web Services - Alat Instance"

#. SLE/patterns-public-cloud-15/patterns-public-cloud-15-Amazon-Web-Services-Instance-Tools/description
msgid ""
"This pattern install the Amazon Web Services instance specific tools which "
"are used to collect instance metadata (e.g. python-ec2metadata)."
msgstr ""
"Pola ini menginstal alat-alat khusus Amazon Web Services (AWS) yang "
"digunakan untuk mengumpulkan metadata instance (misalnya python-ec2metadata)."

#. SLE/patterns-public-cloud-15/patterns-public-cloud-15-Amazon-Web-Services-Tools/summary
msgid "Amazon Web Services - Tools"
msgstr "Amazon Web Services - Alat"

#. SLE/patterns-public-cloud-15/patterns-public-cloud-15-Amazon-Web-Services-Tools/description
msgid ""
"This pattern installs the Amazon Web Services command line interface tools "
"to communicate with the cloud framework (e.g. aws-cli)."
msgstr ""
"Pola ini menginstal alat antarmuka baris perintah Amazon Web Services (AWS) "
"untuk berkomunikasi dengan kerangka kerja cloud (misalnya aws-cli)."

#. SLE/patterns-public-cloud-15/patterns-public-cloud-15-Google-Cloud-Platform/summary
msgid "Google Cloud Platform - All"
msgstr "Google Cloud Platform - Seluruhnya"

#. SLE/patterns-public-cloud-15/patterns-public-cloud-15-Google-Cloud-Platform/description
msgid ""
"This pattern installs all Google Cloud Platform command line interface "
