#. SLE/patterns-public-cloud-15/patterns-public-cloud-15-Google-Cloud-Platform-Instance-Init/summary
msgid "Google Cloud Platform - Instance Initialization"
msgstr "Google Cloud Platform - Inisialisasi Instance"

#. SLE/patterns-public-cloud-15/patterns-public-cloud-15-Google-Cloud-Platform-Instance-Init/description
msgid ""
